> [!WARNING]
{% for s in sensors.edr_isolated %}
> The EDR sensor **{{ s.hostname_short }}** is currently **network-isolated**. This means:
> - The sensor can still communicate with LimaCharlie cloud
> - All other network traffic is blocked
> - Verify if isolation is still needed:
> ```bash
> limacharlie sensor get --sid {{ s.sid }} --oid {{ org.oid }} --output yaml
> ```
> To de-isolate:
> ```bash
> limacharlie sensor rejoin --sid {{ s.sid }} --oid {{ org.oid }}
> ```
{% endfor %}
