---

<details>
<summary><strong>Health Monitoring CLI Commands</strong></summary>

```bash
# List all sensors with status
limacharlie sensor list --oid {{ org.oid }} --output yaml

# Get detailed info for a specific sensor
limacharlie sensor get --sid <SID> --oid {{ org.oid }} --output yaml

# Check sensor connectivity
limacharlie sensor list --oid {{ org.oid }} \
  --filter "[].{sid:sid,hostname:hostname,alive:alive,last_error:last_error}" --output yaml

# List tags for a sensor
limacharlie tag list --sid <SID> --oid {{ org.oid }} --output yaml
```

</details>

